subject: Some Junit related material
msgSnippet: Hi, Could anyone contribute for some useful stuff for Junit starters and tuts for junit extensions. I m interested in combining all those tuts at one place.
messageBody:
Hi,

Could anyone contribute for some useful stuff for Junit starters and
tuts for junit extensions.

I'm interested in combining all those tuts at one place.


Find one at

http://www.eneelesh.com/Tutorials/JUnit_Primer.php


Just to help new people.

Add examples as freely as u can.
